1
00:00:35,620 --> 00:00:38,780
Mast! Lay down the mast!

2
00:00:44,660 --> 00:00:46,340
Hurry up and get the rope!

3
00:00:47,660 --> 00:00:50,340
Bow and stern face the banks! Quick!

4
00:00:54,020 --> 00:00:56,420
Thousands of homes are brightly lit,

5
00:00:56,420 --> 00:00:58,860
and the doors to them are wide open.

6
00:00:58,860 --> 00:01:01,020
This is East Capital.

7
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:04,620
New wine from Sunyang Restaurant!

8
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:07,140
Welcome to enjoy it!

9
00:01:07,300 --> 00:01:09,820
​If you want to know what happens next,

10
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:11,900
wait until next time.

11
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:14,420
People from all over the world gather here,

12
00:01:14,420 --> 00:01:17,380
and envoys from various countries come to communicate with the authorities.

13
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:24,660
[Riverside Code at Qingming Festival]

14
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,660
[Adapted from Ye Wenbiao's Novel Series of the Same Name]

15
00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:27,980
[Episode 13]

16
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:28,880
[Many people today are motivated by fear,]

17
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:29,980
[and few by principles. -Cheng Hao, Northern Song]

18
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:33,400
Wen Yue, right after you left,

19
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,910
Buyou cried his heart out

20
00:01:34,910 --> 00:01:36,680
in the kitchen.

21
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:38,190
So I scolded him,

22
00:01:38,630 --> 00:01:40,230
"What's the point of crying now?

23
00:01:40,230 --> 00:01:42,440
Our ancestors must have done a million good deeds

24
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:44,400
to find you such a perfect wife.

25
00:01:44,590 --> 00:01:45,870
Yet you didn't cherish her."

26
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,400
Aren't you thirsty

27
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,510
from all the talking?

28
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,310
I know you're the best.

29
00:02:03,550 --> 00:02:04,550
Wen Yue.

30
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:06,360
Our family

31
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,620
is about to collapse without you around.

32
00:02:09,750 --> 00:02:11,360
Please come home.

33
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:16,160
What happened between you and my brother?

34
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:21,160
It's my fault.

35
00:02:21,490 --> 00:02:24,240
I've taken so much care of your brother

36
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,880
that he lost ambition.

37
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:28,030
He's worked in the Office of Justice for over a decade

38
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:29,360
without a single promotion.

39
00:02:29,550 --> 00:02:30,830
And he's never around

40
00:02:30,830 --> 00:02:32,360
to run the litigation booth.

41
00:02:33,190 --> 00:02:35,390
I moved out mainly to motivate him.

42
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,800
Don't you feel sorry for me?

43
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:41,280
Won't you let me slack off for a few days?

44
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,720
I feel for you.

45
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,240
I totally do.

46
00:02:44,590 --> 00:02:46,000
Feel free to slack off.

47
00:02:47,670 --> 00:02:48,800
I knew it.

48
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:52,190
You've been supporting this family for years.

49
00:02:52,190 --> 00:02:53,440
Of course, you're tired.

50
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:55,720
But Wen Yue,

51
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:58,160
Mo is getting carpentry work now.

52
00:02:58,160 --> 00:03:00,080
And I've found what I want to do.

53
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,550
We can share your burden from now on.

54
00:03:03,110 --> 00:03:05,110
You found what you want to do?

55
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,030
W-What are you going to do this time?

56
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,000
Wen Yue.

57
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:20,670
You know me.

58
00:03:20,670 --> 00:03:23,240
I'm stronger than the average people

59
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:25,720
and I make a terrible physician.

60
00:03:26,470 --> 00:03:28,390
I've been thinking a lot.

61
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:32,590
I don't necessarily have to practice medicine on someone alive.

62
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:37,080
You won't practice medicine on someone alive?

63
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,440
You want to be a coroner?

64
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,280
I know.

65
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,440
I know this is a bit unconventional.

66
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,470
But I think

67
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:46,030
I'll do much better as a coroner

68
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:47,280
than as a physician.

69
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,670
You've made up your mind?

70
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,390
That's right.

71
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,880
And it's been quite a while.

72
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:58,160
I know there will be criticism

73
00:03:58,160 --> 00:04:00,110
against female coroners.

74
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:03,590
We will not be as respected as our male counterparts.

75
00:04:03,830 --> 00:04:05,640
Don't you mind the criticism?

76
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:06,440
No, I don't.

77
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:09,240
It's not at all easy

78
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,670
to find something I like

79
00:04:10,670 --> 00:04:12,640
and happen to be good at it.

80
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,440
If I'm so easily bothered,

81
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:16,520
then I'll be trapped in the house

82
00:04:16,520 --> 00:04:17,710
sighing over my misfortune.

83
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:19,190
Then go for it.

84
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,430
It's good

85
00:04:21,470 --> 00:04:23,240
to have a life-long pursuit.

86
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:24,870
You have my support.

87
00:04:25,590 --> 00:04:26,520
Really?

88
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:28,820
Wen Yue, don't you think...

89
00:04:28,820 --> 00:04:29,990
No, I don't.

90
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:32,120
You're not breaking any laws.

91
00:04:32,990 --> 00:04:34,270
But if someone

92
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:36,470
gives you a hard time over this,

93
00:04:37,150 --> 00:04:38,310
I'll stand up for you.

94
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:41,710
But there's one problem.

95
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:44,990
It may be difficult for you to get married.

96
00:04:46,470 --> 00:04:48,190
I won't marry anyone.

97
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:51,270
I want to be with you forever.

98
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:53,400
How can you stay single forever?

99
00:04:54,030 --> 00:04:55,870
If someone despises my job,

100
00:04:55,870 --> 00:04:57,800
then he doesn't really like me.

101
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,590
I don't want him.

102
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,470
You've got a point.

103
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:03,870
Wen Yue.

104
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,120
So when will you move back?

105
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:10,960
All right.

106
00:05:11,140 --> 00:05:13,860
You've told me about your new career path.

107
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:15,400
Work hard.

108
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:17,470
When I will move back

109
00:05:17,590 --> 00:05:19,310
depends on Buyou's performance.

110
00:05:20,470 --> 00:05:21,520
Here's a task for you.

111
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:23,240
Go home and monitor him.

112
00:05:26,030 --> 00:05:27,150
Consider it done.

113
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,190
Go ahead.

114
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,270
See you, Wen Yue.

115
00:05:34,030 --> 00:05:34,990
Take care.

116
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:01,120
You've sighed 28 times

117
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:04,030
since we came here.

118
00:06:05,470 --> 00:06:06,360
Why?

119
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:16,120
You know

120
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,710
my wife.

121
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,430
She's so hot-tempered.

122
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:24,750
The orderer is after her,

123
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:27,300
so she wants to take him head-on.

124
00:06:28,150 --> 00:06:29,460
And she told me to stay out of it.

125
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:31,680
When did I want to meddle with it?

126
00:06:32,430 --> 00:06:33,840
But she is my wife.

127
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:36,240
I have to help her.

128
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,080
I can't, though.

129
00:06:41,030 --> 00:06:42,400
Come with me to the Kaifeng Court.

130
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,680
Xiao Yishui was killed.

131
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,800
This is the fatal wound.

132
00:07:01,750 --> 00:07:02,680
It took his life.

133
00:07:02,710 --> 00:07:05,960
The cut is as thin as a cicada's wing and deep.

134
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,800
I don't know what weapon it is.

135
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:09,840
You said the orderer asked to meet Xiao Yishui.

136
00:07:10,750 --> 00:07:12,870
So Xiao Yishui was very likely

137
00:07:13,150 --> 00:07:15,190
killed by that person.

138
00:07:15,190 --> 00:07:16,240
What a pity.

139
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,640
The pier was crowded.

140
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:20,080
I didn't see his face.

141
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,680
You could help your wife

142
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:23,430
by solving the case.

143
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:26,260
Can I solve it?

144
00:07:30,260 --> 00:07:32,000
Why didn't you notify the Kaifeng Court

145
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:35,250
that you and your wife went to the pier?

146
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,400
I didn't want to implicate you.

147
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:42,080
Because I don't believe in this world.

148
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,920
Nor do I trust the ultimate power.

149
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:47,960
I remember you told me...

150
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:50,990
A battle seemingly between fiends

151
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:53,430
could be a power struggle

152
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,080
between the deities.

153
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:57,360
When deities fight,

154
00:07:58,120 --> 00:08:00,430
the mortals better keep their heads down.

155
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:03,030
But if we dare not even look up,

156
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:05,270
how are we any different

157
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:08,120
from the most lowly animals?

158
00:08:08,990 --> 00:08:10,080
It's not easy to live

159
00:08:10,590 --> 00:08:11,680
in this world.

160
00:08:11,990 --> 00:08:14,150
Even petty men are better

161
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,030
than lowly animals.

162
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,840
My father took me

163
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:23,560
to a business center when I was a kid.

164
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:27,120
A group of performers happened

165
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,240
to be playing deities.

166
00:08:30,990 --> 00:08:32,440
My father wouldn't buy me a ticket,

167
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:35,630
so I sneaked in

168
00:08:36,710 --> 00:08:38,120
only to be caught.

169
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,030
They beat me up

170
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:41,200
and threw me out.

171
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:44,030
Then my father told me,

172
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,880
"When deities fight,

173
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,470
we mortals

174
00:08:50,510 --> 00:08:52,030
better not watch it."

175
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:53,680
But you didn't listen to your father.

176
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,560
That's why you got beaten quite often.

177
00:08:57,070 --> 00:08:58,560
And I thought,

178
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,240
"Why can't I watch

179
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:02,150
deities fight?

180
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:05,440
I get beaten up, in the worst case.

181
00:09:05,630 --> 00:09:07,630
Am I not alive and well?"

182
00:09:08,470 --> 00:09:10,060
In a straw cloak...

183
00:09:10,060 --> 00:09:11,810
Spend my life in mist and rain.

184
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:15,240
Better than a saddled horse I like sandals and cane.

185
00:09:16,070 --> 00:09:17,320
Oh, I would fain.

186
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:20,360
I may be a petty man but I'm brave.

187
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:24,880
A petty man who dares to face the deities.

188
00:09:25,710 --> 00:09:26,830
I'll take on

189
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,630
this case.

190
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:29,920
Zhao Buyou.

191
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,560
I have informants in the Kaifeng Court.

192
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:37,360
Two deities are fighting now.

193
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,030
I'm staying put

194
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,560
to not alert anyone.

195
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,920
Stay out of it.

196
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:44,440
I'll investigate secretly.

197
00:09:44,590 --> 00:09:46,360
I'll let you know the result.

198
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,360
Zhao Buyou.

199
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:53,070
I was right about you.

200
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:55,800
For my wife.

201
00:10:01,150 --> 00:10:02,120
And for you.

202
00:10:09,940 --> 00:10:12,620
[Taoyuan Welfare Center, Western Suburb of East Capital]

203
00:10:18,590 --> 00:10:19,760
Taoyuan Welfare Center.

204
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:21,830
Your furniture has arrived.

205
00:10:21,830 --> 00:10:22,630
Coming.

206
00:10:23,590 --> 00:10:24,390
Coming.

207
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:26,560
Mo.

208
00:10:26,610 --> 00:10:27,280
Qiyu.

209
00:10:32,070 --> 00:10:33,680
Mo, thank you for coming

210
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,000
all the way.

211
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:36,630
Here.

212
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:42,360
Qiyu.

213
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,360
Thank you for giving me this carpentry job.

214
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,440
Don't mention it.

215
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:48,830
When you gave me that wood puzzle,

216
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:50,510
I realized how skilled you were.

217
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:52,320
What a delicate puzzle.

218
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,510
Have you solved

219
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:55,630
the puzzle?

220
00:10:56,630 --> 00:10:57,760
I will one day.

221
00:10:58,420 --> 00:10:59,290
Yao He.

222
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:01,120
Why am I

223
00:11:01,590 --> 00:11:03,590
a bit nervous about this apprenticeship?

224
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,070
Your father...

225
00:11:05,510 --> 00:11:05,950
Relax.

226
00:11:05,950 --> 00:11:07,470
My father likes you very much.

227
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:09,470
Just take it easy.

228
00:11:09,590 --> 00:11:11,360
My father may be strict...

229
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,200
Mrs. Xie.

230
00:11:12,210 --> 00:11:13,040
But...

231
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:14,680
Mrs. Xie.

232
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:19,200
Mrs. Xie, where are you going?

233
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,270
What's wrong?

234
00:11:23,470 --> 00:11:24,950
Did Laoba bully you?

235
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,150
Your eyes are swollen.

236
00:11:26,510 --> 00:11:27,270
No.

237
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:30,830
I didn't sleep well last night and my eyes hurt.

238
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,630
Your eyes hurt?

239
00:11:33,470 --> 00:11:35,000
Why don't we sit somewhere

240
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,120
and I'll take a look?

241
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,200
No need, Ban.

242
00:11:38,710 --> 00:11:39,710
I have to go.

243
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,610
Mrs. Xie.

244
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:46,890
Right, Mo.

245
00:11:47,420 --> 00:11:48,280
I'd like you

246
00:11:49,070 --> 00:11:51,000
to tell your sister

247
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,760
and Yao He something.

248
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,200
The tabloid article

249
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:56,150
I promised to write some days ago

250
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:57,630
may not be ready so soon.

251
00:11:58,200 --> 00:12:00,120
The imperial exam is coming up.

252
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:02,120
I have to study for it.

253
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:04,360
You want to take the exam?

254
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:07,070
All scholars

255
00:12:07,070 --> 00:12:08,320
have to pass the exam

256
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:10,000
to join the officialdom.

257
00:12:11,390 --> 00:12:12,630
So many

258
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:14,830
helpless poor people are left unprotected

259
00:12:14,830 --> 00:12:15,710
in this world.

260
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,710
If I can be made an official,

261
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:19,590
I swear I will feed the people

262
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,240
and be someone

263
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:22,920
they can rely on.

264
00:12:25,630 --> 00:12:26,360
Then...

265
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:29,510
Can I also become an official?

266
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:30,760
Of course.

267
00:12:31,680 --> 00:12:32,630
You can totally

268
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,880
join the Ministry of Works

269
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:36,150
with your talent in carpentry.

270
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:38,120
But I'm not aiming

271
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,880
for the Ministry of Works.

272
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:42,270
I'd like to

273
00:12:42,270 --> 00:12:43,920
bring justice to civilians like Bo

274
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:45,200
one day.

275
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:47,390
Since you've decided to join the officialdom,

276
00:12:47,390 --> 00:12:48,590
study hard for the exam.

277
00:12:48,710 --> 00:12:50,710
Shall I introduce you to some mentors?

278
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:53,950
Wait to be called

279
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,590
by the mentors.

280
00:12:55,590 --> 00:12:56,660
[Nanshan Tea House, East Capital]

281
00:12:56,940 --> 00:12:59,460
[Kong Er, Examinee of this year]

282
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:00,560
My apologies.

283
00:13:01,470 --> 00:13:02,270
Song Qiyu.

284
00:13:04,710 --> 00:13:05,760
You'd better watch out.

285
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:08,540
[Nanshan Tea House]

286
00:13:18,810 --> 00:13:19,700
Greetings, mentors.

287
00:13:19,700 --> 00:13:20,440
