00:26:37,120 --> 00:26:38,430
are also very strong.

580
00:26:38,760 --> 00:26:40,840
Amid wind and rain,

581
00:26:41,270 --> 00:26:43,360
or constant floods,

582
00:26:44,120 --> 00:26:45,600
as long as the main beams stand,

583
00:26:45,840 --> 00:26:48,400
the bridge will never collapse.

584
00:26:54,380 --> 00:26:55,720
You're lying.

585
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:57,240
The bridge collapsed.

586
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:59,600
If the main beams are broken,

587
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:02,400
no matter how strong the bridge may be,

588
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:03,840
it will collapse.

589
00:27:05,150 --> 00:27:06,000
All right.

590
00:27:06,360 --> 00:27:07,640
Give it a try.

591
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:08,640
Come on.

592
00:27:09,120 --> 00:27:09,760
Bridge.

593
00:27:10,550 --> 00:27:11,550
What are you doing?

594
00:27:15,910 --> 00:27:16,430
Qiyu.

595
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:25,150
Is something bothering you?

596
00:27:25,430 --> 00:27:25,950
Mo.

597
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:28,840
I need to tell you something.

598
00:27:29,120 --> 00:27:29,950
What is it?

599
00:27:30,430 --> 00:27:31,270
I'm moving.

600
00:27:31,950 --> 00:27:33,030
You're moving?

601
00:27:33,550 --> 00:27:34,950
You might as well guess

602
00:27:35,670 --> 00:27:36,720
where I'm moving to.

603
00:27:43,950 --> 00:27:44,910
Is it tasty?

604
00:27:45,070 --> 00:27:45,950
Yeah.

605
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:50,640
Laoba.

606
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:54,190
Good to see you, Mo, Qiyu.

607
00:27:54,190 --> 00:27:54,840
Come here.

608
00:27:54,840 --> 00:27:55,430
Sit.

609
00:27:58,840 --> 00:28:00,640
Look at all those bags.

610
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:03,950
Are you moving to our shabby streets?

611
00:28:04,190 --> 00:28:05,760
Laoba felt sorry for me

612
00:28:05,760 --> 00:28:07,720
because I was paying so much rent.

613
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:09,670
So he cleared a room for me.

614
00:28:10,600 --> 00:28:11,600
From now on,

615
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:12,760
I will have to

616
00:28:12,760 --> 00:28:14,670
count on you a lot.

617
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:16,430
Don't be so formal.

618
00:28:16,430 --> 00:28:17,130
Yeah.

619
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:18,550
Laoba.

620
00:28:18,760 --> 00:28:20,880
I thought you didn't need extra money.

621
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:22,600
Why are you renting out your room?

622
00:28:23,760 --> 00:28:25,240
So clueless.

623
00:28:25,600 --> 00:28:27,000
Is it about the money?

624
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:30,670
I asked Qiyu to move in.

625
00:28:30,840 --> 00:28:32,310
One day, my house could be

626
00:28:32,670 --> 00:28:34,190
the residence of the top scholar.

627
00:28:35,310 --> 00:28:37,000
What a great insight.

628
00:28:55,720 --> 00:28:56,760
Laoba.

629
00:28:57,550 --> 00:28:59,950
The windows are drafty and leaking.

630
00:29:00,670 --> 00:29:03,360
Can you fix it a bit for Qiyu?

631
00:29:04,600 --> 00:29:06,030
The exam is coming up.

632
00:29:06,030 --> 00:29:07,240
I will just make do.

633
00:29:07,240 --> 00:29:08,400
Besides,

634
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:10,790
Laoba is being very generous.

635
00:29:13,310 --> 00:29:14,240
Qiyu.

636
00:29:14,950 --> 00:29:16,670
Listen to Auntie.

637
00:29:16,910 --> 00:29:18,550
The imperial exam is coming up.

638
00:29:18,550 --> 00:29:19,950
You have to be careful.

639
00:29:19,950 --> 00:29:22,910
Don't go out unless it's necessary.

640
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:25,600
Is it about the ghost examiner, Mrs. Lan?

641
00:29:26,520 --> 00:29:29,000
It's always the same before the exam.

642
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,240
What a cliché.

643
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:32,520
You'd better believe her.

644
00:29:32,910 --> 00:29:35,070
Mrs. Lan never lies.

645
00:29:35,600 --> 00:29:36,880
Listen to me.

646
00:29:37,190 --> 00:29:38,760
I heard that the ghost examiner

647
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:40,310
is nine chi tall.

648
00:29:40,430 --> 00:29:41,790
His face is dark like charcoal.

649
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:44,430
He has no organs under his gown.

650
00:29:44,720 --> 00:29:46,910
He only has a collection

651
00:29:47,270 --> 00:29:49,190
of the hearts of those scholars he killed.

652
00:29:49,550 --> 00:29:51,270
Rumors stop with the wise.

653
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:53,360
Ghosts and deities don't exist.

654
00:29:53,910 --> 00:29:55,310
Even if they do,

655
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:56,910
Qiyu has nothing to do with them.

656
00:29:56,950 --> 00:29:58,150
Don't you know

657
00:29:58,150 --> 00:29:59,950
that it only gets the bad guys?

658
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:01,550
I am so upright.

659
00:30:01,550 --> 00:30:03,360
If he really comes for me...

660
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:05,720
I'll just run away.

661
00:30:07,270 --> 00:30:08,310
Listen to that.

662
00:30:08,310 --> 00:30:09,240
Qiyu.

663
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:11,150
Invite your uncle to sit down

664
00:30:11,150 --> 00:30:13,360
and have some water and nuts.

665
00:30:16,360 --> 00:30:18,360
I'm not familiar with this young man.

666
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:19,580
You got it wrong.

667
00:30:19,580 --> 00:30:20,270
Really?

668
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:22,120
I saw you going back and forth

669
00:30:22,120 --> 00:30:24,120
and I thought you were old acquaintances.

670
00:30:24,840 --> 00:30:25,950
It's just my job.

671
00:30:26,310 --> 00:30:27,310
My job is

672
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:31,030
to keep my employer cozy.

673
00:30:31,270 --> 00:30:32,400
As long as he's cozy.

674
00:30:34,120 --> 00:30:35,310
I haven't paid him yet.

675
00:30:50,150 --> 00:30:51,150
I forgot to pay you.

676
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:06,000
Qiyu.

677
00:31:12,070 --> 00:31:12,950
Wen Yue.

678
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:14,790
What were you doing

679
00:31:14,790 --> 00:31:16,760
at the Great Shop of Mules and Horses last night?

680
00:31:18,270 --> 00:31:20,070
I was at home all night,

681
00:31:20,550 --> 00:31:22,120
preparing to move.

682
00:31:23,070 --> 00:31:24,790
I didn't go to any shops.

683
00:31:25,200 --> 00:31:25,840
Qiyu.

684
00:31:28,210 --> 00:31:30,190
The neighbors said that you moved here.

685
00:31:30,190 --> 00:31:31,600
Why didn't you come say hi?

686
00:31:32,670 --> 00:31:33,430
Buyou.

687
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:36,700
We are neighbors now.

688
00:31:36,950 --> 00:31:38,310
Feel free to tell us

689
00:31:38,310 --> 00:31:39,840
whenever you need something.

690
00:31:41,670 --> 00:31:42,520
Wen Yue.

691
00:31:43,150 --> 00:31:44,360
Why did you come?

692
00:31:44,670 --> 00:31:45,910
Are you here to help?

693
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:51,200
Mo.

694
00:31:51,770 --> 00:31:53,270
Help Qiyu settle in.

695
00:31:56,620 --> 00:31:57,730
Mo, help him.

696
00:32:07,480 --> 00:32:08,030
You're cooking?

697
00:32:08,360 --> 00:32:08,880
All right.

698
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,310
I happen to be hungry.

699
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:13,240
Wen Yue.

700
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:15,240
I asked Inspector Gu to look into it.

701
00:32:15,240 --> 00:32:16,070
That suspect

702
00:32:16,070 --> 00:32:17,430
was working at the bookshop.

703
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:19,240
And the knife he used

704
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:20,670
was his personal belonging.

705
00:32:20,840 --> 00:32:22,000
It was extremely sharp

706
00:32:22,190 --> 00:32:24,190
and cut the paper neatly.

707
00:32:24,190 --> 00:32:26,400
The bookshop owner liked it a lot

708
00:32:26,520 --> 00:32:28,120
and made replicas for all the staff.

709
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:29,400
The shop owner said

710
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:31,550
that this man registered a fake name

711
00:32:31,550 --> 00:32:32,640
and place of origin.

712
00:32:33,310 --> 00:32:34,150
Is there a portrait?

713
00:32:34,840 --> 00:32:35,720
No.

714
00:32:36,550 --> 00:32:37,360
They said

715
00:32:37,360 --> 00:32:38,720
that he was quite peculiar.

716
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:39,950
He didn't bond with

717
00:32:39,950 --> 00:32:40,950
or even greet anyone.

718
00:32:41,270 --> 00:32:42,120
And he

719
00:32:42,120 --> 00:32:44,030
wore a hat all year round

720
00:32:44,150 --> 00:32:45,520
so no one knew how he looked.

721
00:32:47,150 --> 00:32:48,150
Give me the basket.

722
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:51,670
Are you going for groceries?

723
00:32:52,480 --> 00:32:54,490
We actually make a great team.

724
00:32:54,880 --> 00:32:56,050
We worked so well together

725
00:32:56,050 --> 00:32:57,270
at the bookshop yesterday.

726
00:33:00,190 --> 00:33:01,550
What are you doing?

727
00:33:01,550 --> 00:33:02,640
I'm returning to the umbrella shop.

728
00:33:03,030 --> 00:33:04,360
Take care of everyone.

729
00:33:24,700 --> 00:33:28,580
[Top Scholar]

730
00:33:42,310 --> 00:33:42,880
No way.

731
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:43,240
Qiyu...

732
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,070
Mr. Jian.

733
00:34:04,310 --> 00:34:05,270
Director Zhang.

734
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:08,680
I'm here to see Qiyu off.

735
00:34:09,030 --> 00:34:10,550
What were you...

736
00:34:11,640 --> 00:34:12,640
It was nothing.

737
00:34:12,640 --> 00:34:14,880
Qiyu is under a lot of pressure.

738
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,790
Please help ease his mind.

739
00:34:19,790 --> 00:34:20,920
Qiyu.

740
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:22,470
Director Zhang and I

741
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:24,020
will wait for you at the door.

742
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:45,360
Qiyu.

743
00:34:45,710 --> 00:34:46,790
You're going to the exam.

744
00:34:47,200 --> 00:34:49,200
My family and I made this Top-Scholar Cake

745
00:34:49,200 --> 00:34:50,710
for you last night.

746
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:52,640
We wish you the best and great success

747
00:34:52,640 --> 00:34:53,600
in this imperial exam.

748
00:34:53,960 --> 00:34:54,790
Try it.

749
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:00,160
Thank you.

750
00:35:02,070 --> 00:35:02,920
What's wrong?

751
00:35:03,640 --> 00:35:04,750
Are you nervous?

752
00:35:04,750 --> 00:35:05,710
Or did you

753
00:35:05,710 --> 00:35:07,360
get scolded by the mentors again?

754
00:35:09,120 --> 00:35:09,710
No.

755
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:11,990
Qiyu.

756
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,440
Don't be nervous.

757
00:35:13,790 --> 00:35:15,070
You will definitely

758
00:35:15,470 --> 00:35:16,640
do well in the exam.

759
00:35:16,990 --> 00:35:18,310
Have your pen and ink?

760
00:35:18,470 --> 00:35:19,750
Don't forget anything.

761
00:35:21,510 --> 00:35:22,790
Let's go. I'll see you off.

762
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:53,680
Song Qiyu.

763
00:35:54,960 --> 00:35:57,510
Among the examinees of this year,

764
00:35:57,680 --> 00:35:59,160
you are my favorite

765
00:35:59,270 --> 00:36:02,160
who I cherish like my own disciple.

766
00:36:02,550 --> 00:36:03,640
Today,

767
00:36:03,640 --> 00:36:05,710
I hired a donkey cart for you

768
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:08,550
to save you the trouble of traveling.

769
00:36:09,160 --> 00:36:10,200
Hop on.

770
00:36:11,930 --> 00:36:13,120
Don't forget

771
00:36:13,860 --> 00:36:15,400
what I taught you.

772
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,230
Qiyu.

773
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:29,070
Have a piece

774
00:36:29,370 --> 00:36:30,600
of the Top-Scholar Cake.

775
00:36:33,270 --> 00:36:34,230
Once you take a bite,

776
00:36:34,230 --> 00:36:35,370
you'll be the top scholar.

777
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:36,600
Here.

778
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:54,160
I'll wait for the good news.

779
00:36:57,820 --> 00:37:00,100
[Top Scholar]

780
00:37:03,700 --> 00:37:04,510
[Wen's Umbrella Shop]

781
00:37:04,510 --> 00:37:06,000
Your umbrella looks nice.

782
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:06,640
Right?

783
00:37:07,310 --> 00:37:08,840
Bring them for repair or replacement

784
00:37:08,840 --> 00:37:11,200
if there is any problem with the umbrellas.

785
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:12,790
- Okay. Thank you. - Okay.

786
00:37:14,160 --> 00:37:15,200
It's so delicate.

787
00:37:15,200 --> 00:37:15,990
Absolutely.

788
00:38:12,120 --> 00:38:13,920
Wen Yue, are you hungry?

789
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:14,990
I'm late.

790
00:38:35,710 --> 00:38:36,440
Help!

791
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:37,160
Hurry!

792
00:38:37,160 --> 00:38:38,030
Bad guy here!

793
00:38:38,030 --> 00:38:38,770
- Bad guy here! - Let's go.

794
00:38:38,770 --> 00:38:39,160
Hurry.

795
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:39,640
Hurry.

796
00:38:39,640 --> 00:38:40,650
[Wen's Umbrella Shop]
Catch him.

797
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:42,130
Hurry, catch him.

798
00:38:43,200 --> 00:38:43,680
Hurry.

799
00:38:45,750 --> 00:38:46,400
Stop there!

800
00:38:47,030 --> 00:38:47,600
Stop!

801
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:48,640
Are you fine?

802
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,470
Are you hurt?

803
00:38:49,710 --> 00:38:50,680
I-I'm fine.

804
00:38:52,920 --> 00:38:53,600
Hurry.

805
00:38:53,820 --> 00:38:54,920
I'll bandage it for you.

806
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:55,450
Let's go.

807
00:38:57,550 --> 00:39:00,640
Wen Yue, you really have foresight.

808
00:39:01,070 --> 00:39:02,730
The orderer we're tracking down

809
00:39:03,290 --> 00:39:05,230
came for you at the umbrella shop.

810
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:10,510
Wen Yue.

811
00:39:10,510 --> 00:39:12,470
It's okay. I'm almost done.

812
00:39:19,230 --> 00:39:21,310
He may come back at any time.

813
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:24,270
You can't live here by yourself anymore.

814
00:39:25,120 --> 00:39:26,840
Let me move in with you.

815
00:39:29,880 --> 00:39:30,880
Nonsense.

816
00:39:32,130 --> 00:39:33,300
Don't come here lately.

817
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:39,360
If he comes back

818
00:39:39,990 --> 00:39:41,400
and the officers can't make it,

819
00:39:42,200 --> 00:39:43,360
what will you do?

820
00:39:47,070 --> 00:39:48,600
I'll kill him with a kitchen knife.

821
00:39:54,030 --> 00:39:55,680
If I had been a bit slower,

822
00:39:56,160 --> 00:39:58,680
you'd be lying in the mortuary of the Kaifeng Court now.

823
00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:06,840
Zhao Buyou.

824
00:40:09,790 --> 00:40:11,230
I will accept my fate if I lose.

825
00:40:11,510 --> 00:40:12,920
Who gave you the right?

826
00:40:13,230 --> 00:40:14,510
This is our fate.

827
00:40:15,550 --> 00:40:17,120
We must win.

828
00:40:19,320 --> 00:40:20,620
Risking two lives

829
00:40:20,790 --> 00:40:22,340
to take him down is too much.

830
00:40:24,510 --> 00:40:26,200
I promised Inspector Gu

831
00:40:26,310 --> 00:40:27,960
to help him solve this case.

832
00:40:28,550 --> 00:40:29,510
All right.

833
00:40:30,200 --> 00:40:31,840
Then I don't have to protect you.

834
00:40:33,550 --> 00:40:35,750
You are just a useless scholar

835
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:37,600
who can't help with anything

836
00:40:38,710 --> 00:40:40,270
and only annoys me.

837
00:40:51,160 --> 00:40:52,840
I know why you're saying that.

838
00:40:53,790 --> 00:40:55,960
You just want to make me angry

839
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:57,360
and hurt my feelings

840
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:58,470
so that I leave.

841
00:41:00,030 --> 00:41:00,990
You win.

842
00:41:01,750 --> 00:41:03,470
It did hurt my feelings.

843
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:05,960
Leave.

844
00:41:26,550 --> 00:41:27,750
My father asked me

845
00:41:28,200 --> 00:41:29,960
to practice martial arts when I was a kid

846
00:41:30,550 --> 00:41:32,030
but I didn't listen to him.

847
00:41:35,070 --> 00:41:36,640
Now I regret it so much.

848
00:42:19,980 --> 00:42:28,340
[Wen's Umbrella Shop]

849
00:43:02,060 --> 00:43:03,540
[Fashion in Song Dynasty]

850
00:43:03,540 --> 00:43:05,220
[Song Dynastypedia]

851
00:43:05,220 --> 00:43:07,220
[The Hat Demon had a historical prototype. Illustrated by Lin Jiachuan]

852
00:43:07,680 --> 00:43:10,130
There turned out to be a Hat Demon in the Song Dynasty.

853
00:43:10,810 --> 00:43:13,780
It is said that there was a monster in the shape of a hat

854
00:43:13,920 --> 00:43:15,360
that ate people

855
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:19,500
and did city walks in Luoyang and East Capital at night.

856
00:43:20,030 --> 00:43:21,980
The Hat Demon caused

857
00:43:21,980 --> 00:43:24,330
great panic and chaos across the nation.

858
00:43:25,070 --> 00:43:27,930
Clan members or neighbors

859
00:43:28,380 --> 00:43:30,120
gathered at night,

860
00:43:30,200 --> 00:43:31,640
chatting until dawn

861
00:43:31,640 --> 00:43:33,880
to expel or avoid the Hat Demon.

862
00:43:34,180 --> 00:43:35,620
[Kill the Hat Demon]
This seemingly

863
00:43:35,620 --> 00:43:37,580
absurd rumor about the Hat Demon

864
00:43:37,960 --> 00:43:41,320
gradually subsided under the investigation and suppression

865
00:43:41,320 --> 00:43:43,320
of Emperor Zhenzong.

866
00:43:43,320 --> 00:43:45,790
Just tell me if you're curious about

867
00:43:45,790 --> 00:43:48,880
where the Hat Demon hid.

868
00:44:06,300 --> 00:44:09,300
